<div class="splashform">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
      <div class="text-center animated flipInX">
        <%= link_to root_path do %>
          <%= image_tag('aytext.png', :alt => "Brand", :class => "inline-block pageimage") %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading"><h3>Know What You Share</h3></div>
        <div class="panel-body">
        	<h5>Apply Yourself is serious about privacy.</h5>
          <p><i>Though this is an online learning community, we all need personal space.</i></p>
          <p> When you build a practice resume or apply for jobs, you are sharing your writing with other users.  Otherwise, what's yours is <strong>only</strong> yours.  That includes:</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="list-group">
